description:
This is a 11 minute workout called 'WIN Row' from the channel Aisyah Rafaee.
The workout falls under Cardio/Indoor rowing.
It's suitable for Advanced fitness levels.
You'll need Rower for this workout.
The workout has a The Meditative Grind and The Warrior Workout vibe.
The The Meditative Grind vibe means Zone in, lock down, let repetition take over. This is especially good for Those who love a slow burn and rhythmic intensity. The The Warrior Workout vibe means Unleash your inner beast. Sweat-dripping, heart-pounding, primal energy. This is especially good for Days when you want to destroy stress and feel invincible..
The technique difficulty is Intermediate.
The effort required is Challenging.

Original workout description: Channel your energy and sharpen your focus with Aisyah. As you move through each stroke, you'll concentrate on the theme of WIN—"what's important now?"—helping you to refocus and prioritize. This session is all about harnessing the power of the present moment to achieve clarity and drive, both on and off the water. Ready to row? Let's get after it! Max rhythm: 32, Format: HIIT...
